  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA29">
<l>ivaraip poruḷuṇara māṭṭātā rellā</l>
<l>mivarai yikaḻvatē kaṇṭī - rivartamatu</l>
<l>pūkkōla mēṉip poṭipūci yeṉpaṇinta</l>
<l>pēykkōlaṅ kaṇṭār piṟar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All those who cannot perceive him as meaning</l>
<l>slight him, see. His body of flower beauty</l>
<l>adorned with bones, smeared with ashes</l>
<l>others see [his] demonic beauty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
